    </div>


    <div class="row" style="margin-top: 40px">
        <label>输入地址「一行一个」</label>
        <textarea id="addresses" rows="10" style="width: 100%"></textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6" style="padding: 0">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary" id="submit" style="margin-top: 10px">提交</button>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6" style="padding: 0">
            <div class="input-group mb-3" style="margin-top: 10px">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                    <span class="input-group-text" id="threshold_text">BNB数量</span>
                </div>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="threshold" aria-describedby="basic-addon3" value="0.015">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <ul>
        <li>本工具代码本地执行，请放心使用</li>
        <li>请不要留有空白行</li>
        <li>根据 BNB 数量向账户发送 BNB，当总地址小于这个数量的时候将终止发送程序</li>
        <li>在发送前请将燃料费考虑在内</li>
        <li>捐赠地址: 0xD1B260aba3bA6f3D3099725b1b1C7cdD12581974</li>
    </ul>

    <table class="table" style="margin-top: 10px">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">#</th>
            <th scope="col">TX</th>
            <th scope="col">地址</th>
            <th scope="col">状态</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="hex">
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<div style="height: 30px;margin-top: 70px">

</div>
